These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Hobby: photography, baking
Job: lawyer, firefighter
1. Job:lawyer is in an even position##4
2. Job:firefighter == Hobby:baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | baking | photography |
| Job     | firefighter    | lawyer   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Beverage: milk, 7up
Sport: skiing, biathlon
1. Sport:skiing is in an odd position##4
2. Beverage:7up is on the left of Beverage:milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | 7up | milk        |
| Sport      | skiing  | biathlon |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
